Math/MathML"><mi>x</mi><mo>=E2=89=A5</mo><mn>4</mn></math></mjx-assistive-m=
ml></mjx-container> can be achieved in several ways.</p>
<p>We can use a number line as shown in Figure 2.&nbsp;The blue ray begins =
at <mjx-container class=3D"MathJax CtxtMenu_Attached_0" jax=3D"CHTML" tabin=
dex=3D"0" ctxtmenu_counter=3D"1" style=3D"font-size: 109.4%; position: rela=
tive;"><mjx-math class=3D"MJX-TEX" aria-hidden=3D"true"><mjx-mi class=3D"mj=
