/p>
<p class=3D"wp-caption-text"><b>Figure 2</b></p>
</div>
<p>We can use <strong>set-builder notation</strong>: <mjx-container class=
=3D"MathJax CtxtMenu_Attached_0" jax=3D"CHTML" tabindex=3D"0" ctxtmenu_coun=
ter=3D"2" style=3D"font-size: 109.4%; position: relative;"><mjx-math class=
