3.org/1998/Math/MathML"><mi>x</mi><mo>=E2=89=A5</mo><mn>4</mn></math></mjx-=
assistive-mml></mjx-container> are represented as <mjx-container class=3D"M=
athJax CtxtMenu_Attached_0" jax=3D"CHTML" tabindex=3D"0" ctxtmenu_counter=
=3D"4" style=3D"font-size: 109.4%; position: relative;"><mjx-math class=3D"=
